sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor C as Clinician
    participant FE as Frontend<br/>(Streamlit)
    participant O as Orchestrator<br/>(Go REST API)
    participant LB as Load Balancer<br/>(Go L7 reverse proxy)
    participant SC as Service<br/>ai-worker-cpu
    participant SG as Service<br/>ai-worker-gpu
    participant WC as Worker pod<br/>(CPU)
    participant WG as Worker pod<br/>(GPU)
    participant PV as models-pv<br/>(PersistentVolume)

    C->>FE: Upload fundus image, pick model
    FE->>O: POST /api/demo/predict<br/>(multipart: file, model_name)

    rect rgb(245,245,220)
    note over O: Validation chain<br/>(before forwarding)
    O->>O: 1. size cap (limit+1 read) -> 413 if too big
    O->>O: 2. declared Content-Type in allowlist -> 415
    O->>O: 3. magic-byte sniff (DetectContentType) -> 415
    O->>O: 4. header-only DecodeConfig<br/>(decompression-bomb guard) -> 413
    O->>O: 5. sanitize model_name (regex, no '..') -> 400
    end

    O->>LB: POST /predict/ (forwarded)

    alt Content-Length < SIZE_THRESHOLD (small image)
        LB->>LB: log [route] ... -> CPU
        LB->>SC: ReverseProxy to CPU_BACKEND
        SC->>WC: kube-proxy picks a Ready pod (L4)
        WC->>PV: get_model(name) [cache miss only]
        PV-->>WC: model bytes (.h5 / .keras)
        WC->>WC: preprocess 224x224x3 + normalize
        WC->>WC: model.predict(x)
        WC-->>SC: {status, probability, node_type=Standard CPU,<br/>worker_id, execution_time}
        SC-->>LB: response
    else Content-Length >= SIZE_THRESHOLD (large image)
        LB->>LB: log [route] ... -> GPU
        LB->>SG: ReverseProxy to GPU_BACKEND
        SG->>WG: kube-proxy picks a Ready pod (L4)
        WG->>PV: get_model(name) [cache miss only]
        PV-->>WG: model bytes
        WG->>WG: preprocess + model.predict(x)
        WG-->>SG: {status, probability, node_type=High-Performance GPU,<br/>worker_id, execution_time}
        SG-->>LB: response
    end

    LB-->>O: upstream JSON
    O-->>FE: {orchestrator:{validated, routed_to_pool}, upstream:{...}}
    FE-->>C: probability % + clinical band<br/>(Low / Suspicious / High Risk) + telemetry
